data.description: This Sun City beauty is in a prime location and move in ready! Your new home features charming curb appeal, an extended back patio where you can enjoy golf course views without the golf lot premium. The heart of the home is the updated kitchen with maple cabinets & corian counters, newer wood plank tile, breakfast bar and newer appliances. The home boasts formal living and dining as well as a family room space, 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 fully updated bathrooms, lots of storage, indoor laundry, newer vinyl dual-pane windows, air conditioned workshop, 1 car garage with opener plus a golf cart garage. Select furnishings can be purchased on separate bill of sale. Sun City is a 55+ age-restricted community.
